---
import Container from "../../shared/Container.astro";
import Paragraph from "../../shared/Paragraph.astro";
import Subtitle from "../../shared/Subtitle.astro";
---

<section class="p-10 bg-light">
    <Container className="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <Subtitle className="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-dark mb-4">
                Nuestro Proceso de Analítica
            </Subtitle>
            <Paragraph className="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                Metodología probada para convertir datos en crecimiento empresarial
            </Paragraph>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
            <div class="text-center">
                <div
                    class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 text-2xl font-bold">
                    1
                </div>
                <Subtitle className="text-xl font-bold text-dark mb-3">
                    Auditoría Inicial
                </Subtitle>
                <Paragraph className="text-gray-600">
                   Analizamos tu situación actual, herramientas existentes y objetivos de negocio para crear una estrategia personalizada.
                </Paragraph>
            </div>

            <div class="text-center">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-yellow-400 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 text-2xl font-bold">
                    2
                </div>
                <Subtitle className="text-xl font-bold text-dark mb-3">Configuración</Subtitle>
                <Paragraph className="text-gray-600">
                    Implementamos las herramientas de analítica, configuramos eventos y establecemos los KPIs más relevantes.
                </Paragraph>
            </div>

            <div class="text-center">
                <div
                    class="w-16 h-16 bg-green-400 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 text-2xl font-bold">
                    3
                </div>
                <Subtitle className="text-xl font-bold text-dark mb-3">Monitoreo</Subtitle>
                <Paragraph className="text-gray-600">
                    Recopilamos y analizamos datos continuamente, identificando patrones y oportunidades de mejora.
                </Paragraph>
            </div>

            <div class="text-center">
                <div
                    class="w-16 h-16 bg-purple-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 text-2xl font-bold">
                    4
                </div>
                <Subtitle className="text-xl font-bold text-dark mb-3">Optimización</Subtitle>
                <Paragraph className="text-gray-600">
                    Implementamos mejoras basadas en datos y medimos el impacto para asegurar el crecimiento continuo.
                </Paragraph>
            </div>
        </div>
    </Container>
</section>
<section class="my-10">
    <Container>
        <div class="w-full relative py-8 md:py-10 px-6 md:px-8 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-tr from-gray-100 to-gray-200 dark:from-gray-900 dark:to-transparent">
            <div class="absolute right-0 top-0 h-full w-full flex justify-end">
                <div class="w-28 h-28 overflow-auto flex rounded-xl relative blur-2xl">
                    <span
                        class="absolute w-16 h-16 -top-1 -right-1 bg-green-500 rounded-md rotate-45"></span>
                    <span
                        class="absolute w-16 h-16 -bottom-1 -right-1 bg-[#FCDC58] rounded-md rotate-45"></span>
                    <span
                        class="absolute w-16 h-16 -bottom-1 -left-1 bg-primary rounded-md rotate-45"></span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="absolute left-0 bottom-0 h-full w-full flex items-end">
                <div class="w-28 h-28 overflow-auto flex rounded-xl relative blur-2xl">
                    <span
                        class="absolute w-16 h-16 -top-1 -right-1 bg-green-500 rounded-md rotate-45"></span>
                    <span
                        class="absolute w-16 h-16 -bottom-1 -right-1 bg-[#FCDC58] rounded-md rotate-45"></span>
                    <span
                        class="absolute w-16 h-16 -bottom-1 -left-1 bg-primary rounded-md rotate-45"></span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mx-auto text-center max-w-xl md:max-w-2xl relative">
                <Subtitle
                    className="text-3xl/tight sm:text-4xl/tight md:text-5xl/tight font-bold text-heading-1">
                    Auditoría Gratuita de 
                    <span  class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-600 from-20% via-primary via-30% to-green-600">
                        Analítica Digital</span>
                </Subtitle>
                <Paragraph className="md:text-lg text-heading-3 pt-10">
                    Descubre qué datos estás perdiendo y cómo optimizar tu estrategia digital
                </Paragraph>
                <div class="mx-auto max-w-md sm:max-w-xl pt-10">
                    <a href="#">
                        <button
                            type="button"
                            class="px-6 py-3 rounded-full outline-none overflow-hidden border duration-300 ease-linear
                            after:absolute after:inset-x-0 after:aspect-square after:scale-0 after:opacity-70 after:origin-center after:duration-300 after:ease-linear after:rounded-full after:top-0 after:left-0 after:bg-[#172554]
                            bg-primary border-transparent relative  hover:border-[#172554] hover:after:opacity-100 hover:after:scale-[2.5] cursor-pointer"
                        >
                            <span class="text-white relative z-[5]">Contactar</span>
                        </button>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </Container>
</section>

